{"id":"7912","name":"HiRes Twitter","tagline":"Download public or private Twitter media at highest quality, share or save to Photos or Files","icon":"ios14 c4292093695 g59841","latest":"34751","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>OS</th>\n<th>Compatibility</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>macOS</td>\n<td>No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>iOS 15 or higher</td>\n<td>Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>iOS 14 or lower</td>\n<td>Yes</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em>HiRes Twitter</em> can download media from public or <strong>private</strong> accounts at the highest quality, save to <em>Photos</em> or <em>Files</em> or share. It can also upload images at up to 8K.</p>\n<h2>Downloading Media</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Long-press</strong> a tweet’s share button, then select <em>HiRes Twitter</em> from the list.<ul>\n<li>Alternatively you can tap the share button, tap ‘Share via’, then select <em>HiRes Twitter</em>. This may not work on private tweets, though.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Images are downloaded at up to 8K (for comparison, the Twitter app is limited to 4K).</li>\n<li>gifs can be downloaded as gif and/or mp4. Since Twitter stores submitted gifs as mp4, this shortcut uses the same algorithm as <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/10377/\"><em>Better GIF Maker</em></a>‘s to obtain maximum gif quality (optional).</li>\n<li>You can save media to <em>iCloud</em> or <em>On My Device</em> on iOS 15, or to <em>iCloud/Shortcuts</em> on iOS 14 or older.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"Sample Screen\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bJzhC0F.png\"></p>\n<h2>Uploading Images</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To compose a tweet with images at up to 8K (for comparison, the Twitter app is limited to 4K), run <em>HiRes Twitter</em> from the <em>Shortcuts</em> app.</li>\n<li>If you share your own tweet, you can reply to it with images.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>User Settings</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You can change user settings by running <em>HiRes Twitter</em> from the <em>Shortcuts</em> app.</li>\n<li>Connecting accounts enables you to download private media and upload images.</li>\n<li>To change folder or album, toggle the <em>Save to Files/Photos</em> option off and on.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"Sample Screen\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IyhdOnA.png\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>2.5.4 - Aug. 30, 2022, 12:14 p.m.</strong></p><p>2022-08-30<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;• Name change from HiRes Tweet to HiRes Twitter<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;• Major fixes for Arabic users (من فضلك أخبرني إذا وجدت أي مشكلة)<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;• Usability enhancements</p>"}